SUMMARY:Flight Study – Day 1: Checklists + ABCD
DESCRIPTION:Focus: Checklist discipline and ABCD flow.\n- Say “Checklist start / Checklist complete” for Preflight\, Run-up\, Before-Takeoff\, Pre-Maneuver\, Before-Landing.\n- Practice ABCD engine failure flow (Airspeed → Best Field → Checklist → Declare) to ≤10 seconds.\n- Review engine restart steps: Carb heat ON\, Fuel BOTH\, Mixture RICH\, Throttle 1/4\, Primer IN/LOCKED\, Mags BOTH.
END:VEVENT

