SUMMARY:Flight Study – Day 5: Emergency Procedures
DESCRIPTION:Focus: Engine failures and field choice.\n- Repeat ABCD flow and restart checklist.\n- Practice choosing a best field quickly and committing.\n- Imagine MAYDAY / 7700 calls and what you actually say.\n- Optional: Use map/Google Earth to practice picking fields around KFXE.
END:VEVENT

