SUMMARY:Flight Study – Day 6: Integrated Scenario
DESCRIPTION:Focus: Full flight mental run.\n- Simulate: Preflight → Taxi → Run-up → Departure (no talking) → Maneuvers (with pre-maneuver checklist) → Engine-out ABCD → Return to field.\n- Include radio calls and frequency changes.\n- Visualize staying ahead of the airplane the whole time.
END:VEVENT

